1. CREATE MAIL
	GET the question for today
	BUILD the email to go to players
	SEND the email
	
2. READ AND PARSE PLAYER RESPONSES
	GET responses from each player
	PARSE the answers from the response
	PUT into record for each player
	
3. GRADING/SCORING
	GET all responses for all players who answered the questions
	SHOW responses in a table with the ability to edit responses
	UPDATE player with the grade that player received for his/her given answer